column5: Yeah Joe I saw this in the morning news, pretty funny...
I wear one of those sometimes when I'm gardening.
It keeps the satellites from scanning my thoughts!!!!!
Awesome!!!!  I always loved the open letter to the Kansas school board from the Church of the Flying Spaghetti Monster.
This 'NUT' will come over and claim refugee status due to religious prosecution!
He is not a nut.  He is a joker.  Look up the open letter to the Kansas School Board by The Church of the Flying Spaghetti Monster and you will get a better idea of what this is about.
This is awesome.  Good on him.
love it  Lifes too short to take seriously.
Paul using a plastic strainer is considered spatulaism in his religion and is punishable by 50 lashes with a wet noodle and told to fork off
PASTAFARIAN MUSIC....REGGAE OR RAGGU?    <iframe width="560" height="349" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/l3WPKznFvfk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>

Macaronians like myself, practice Spatualism on the second sunday of each Noodle.Much like Rigatoniists. except we use the nonstick teflon spatulas, they use the rubber/silicone variety.  Nanou Nanou.
He could wear a rhinestone tiara for all I care, as long as he's a safe driver. But don't get me started on that issue...
